            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Herculi Saxsano <note>sic</note> <lb n="2"/>sacrum Iulius Vi<lb break="no" n="3"/>ctor |(centurio) pro se et <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan><lb break="no" n="4"/>militones si<lb break="no" n="5"/>ngulares pedite<lb break="no" n="6"/>s Acili Strabonis <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: nach dem Suffektkonsulat des L. Acilius Strabo im Jahr 80 n. Chr. (B): Matijević: Z. 6: Straboni[s].</p>
            </div>
